org.anchoranalysis.plugin.image.task.bean.grouped.raster

Class GroupedMeanChannelTask

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<Task<T,S>>
      • Task<ProvidesStackInput,GroupedSharedState<S,T>>
        • GroupedStackBase<Channel,RunningSumChannel>
          • GroupedMeanChannelTask

  • public class GroupedMeanChannelTask
extends GroupedStackBase<Channel,RunningSumChannel>
    Creates a an aggregated-image for each group, where each voxel-value is the mean voxel-value across the group.

    The following outputs are produced:

    Output NameDefault?Description
    meanyesAn image with the mean pixel value across all images, for each channel.
    inherited from Task
    Author:
